## Next Steps for Deployment
To enable Vercel Web Analytics in your deployment:
1. Navigate to your Vercel dashboard's Analytics section
2. Click the "Enable" button to activate Web Analytics
3. Deploy your application (`vercel deploy`)
4. Verify by checking the browser's Network tab for requests from `/<unique-path>/view`

